<item>
            <title>[PIG-1806] Modify embedded Pig API for usability </title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/PIG-1806</link>
                <project id="12310730" key="PIG">Pig</project>
                    <description>&lt;ul&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;bind methods. Currently, to explicitly bind variables to parameters, the variable type must be string:&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;


&lt;div class=&quot;code panel&quot; style=&quot;border-width: 1px;&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;codeContent panelContent&quot;&gt;
&lt;pre class=&quot;code-java&quot;&gt;
&lt;span class=&quot;code-keyword&quot;&gt;public&lt;/span&gt; BoundScript bind(Map&amp;lt;&lt;span class=&quot;code-object&quot;&gt;String&lt;/span&gt;, &lt;span class=&quot;code-object&quot;&gt;String&lt;/span&gt;&amp;gt; vars) &lt;span class=&quot;code-keyword&quot;&gt;throws&lt;/span&gt; IOException {...}
&lt;/pre&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt; 

&lt;p&gt;User needs explicitly convert variables to strings before passing them in. We propose to change the method signature so user does not need to do the conversion:&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;div class=&quot;code panel&quot; style=&quot;border-width: 1px;&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;codeContent panelContent&quot;&gt;
&lt;pre class=&quot;code-java&quot;&gt;
&lt;span class=&quot;code-keyword&quot;&gt;public&lt;/span&gt; BoundScript bind(Map&amp;lt;&lt;span class=&quot;code-object&quot;&gt;String&lt;/span&gt;, &lt;span class=&quot;code-object&quot;&gt;Object&lt;/span&gt;&amp;gt; vars) &lt;span class=&quot;code-keyword&quot;&gt;throws&lt;/span&gt; IOException {...}
&lt;/pre&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt; 

&lt;p&gt;Internally Pig uses toString() method to convert variables to strings.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;ul&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;fs method. Current Pig.fs(...) method doesn&apos;t return any value. Since this method just turns around to call FsShell.run() which has a return code, we should pass this return code to the user;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;


&lt;div class=&quot;code panel&quot; style=&quot;border-width: 1px;&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;codeContent panelContent&quot;&gt;
&lt;pre class=&quot;code-java&quot;&gt;
&lt;span class=&quot;code-keyword&quot;&gt;public&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&quot;code-keyword&quot;&gt;static&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&quot;code-object&quot;&gt;int&lt;/span&gt; fs(&lt;span class=&quot;code-object&quot;&gt;String&lt;/span&gt; cmd) &lt;span class=&quot;code-keyword&quot;&gt;throws&lt;/span&gt; IOException {...}
&lt;/pre&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;</description>
